title: cFosSpeed 9.62 Build 2135 Final
description:
cFosSpeed - this is a network driver, which is tied to your existing Internet connection and optimizes data transfer by means of traffic prioritizing.

Installation:
1) Install cFosSpeed 
2) Use automatic reset trial or use a manual reset
Autoreset - automatically adds a 30-day trial license when you start your computer. Will begin only when the trial license has expired.
Reset only - manually adds a 30-day trial license and remove automated process reset.

Interface language - English, Russian and others
